{{page-title "Documentation — Companies"}}
<div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl py-6 px-4 space-y-6">

  <Panel::Card>
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Companies</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
      A Company record groups all Career Caddy resources related to a single employer —
      job posts, applications, scrapes, scores, and questions. When you're tracking multiple
      roles at the same company, the company profile gives you a single place to see everything.
    </p>
    {{!-- <img src="" alt="screenshot of a company profile page" /> --}}
  </Panel::Card>

  <Panel::Card>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Automatic vs. Manual Creation</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
      Companies are created automatically when you add a Job Post with a company name. You
      don't need to create them separately. If two job posts share the same company name, they
      link to the same company record.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
      You can also create a company manually if you want to start tracking before you have
      a specific role to add.
    </p>
  </Panel::Card>

  <Panel::Card>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">What's Tracked Per Company</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 text-sm list-disc list-inside">
      <li><strong>Job Posts</strong> — all roles you've saved from this employer</li>
      <li><strong>Applications</strong> — your history of applying there</li>
      <li><strong>Scrapes</strong> — raw captures of their job pages</li>
      <li><strong>Scores</strong> — how well you fit their roles</li>
      <li><strong>Questions &amp; Answers</strong> — interview questions specific to this company</li>
      <li><strong>Notes</strong> — anything worth keeping about the company itself</li>
    </ul>
    {{!-- <img src="" alt="screenshot of company profile showing the resource tabs" /> --}}
  </Panel::Card>

  <Panel::Card>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Example Company Profile</h2>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded p-4 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <div><span class="font-semibold">Name:</span> Acme Corp</div>
      <div><span class="font-semibold">Notes:</span> Series C startup, ~180 employees, strong eng culture. Offices in Austin and remote. Glassdoor 4.1.</div>
      <div class="pt-1 space-y-1">
        <div class="font-semibold">Linked resources:</div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 pl-2 space-y-1">
          <li>3 job posts</li>
          <li>1 active application (Phone Screen)</li>
          <li>2 scrapes</li>
          <li>1 score (87/100)</li>
          <li>4 interview questions</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    {{!-- <img src="" alt="screenshot of the example company record" /> --}}
  </Panel::Card>

</div>
